metadata.description:
in an interview, the big queen ancestar maya angelou guides us to see defeat as a necessary feeling because it teaches us how to move through it and fail forward. she is the joyous sage at the beginning of this .wav 

magnetic[ mag-net-ik ]
adjective; 
1. of or relating to a magnet or magnetism.
2. having the properties of a magnet.
3. capable of being magnetized or attracted by a magnet.
4. pertaining to the magnetic field of the earth
5. exerting a strong attractive power or charm: a magnetic personality.

 the last song in the laws of the universe series 
 abundance
 infinite 
 and now, expressing the law of attraction: magnetic 

light attracts like 
and repulses others. 
this song calls us to be grounded in our truest selves and to allow our greatness, uniqueness, and power to prevail because that what continues to magnetize the reality we desire. 

written and performed by charm taylor
co-produced by charm taylor and infinite i
mixed and mastered by cam murdoch 
visual art by a.i.irl charm 

closing 2022 in reflection and gratitude

opening 2023  
with everything we need in place, 

charm
